{
  "stem": "18960.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was on the transport of volunteers to-- to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I went-- in the station, I-- I left the train to have a-- have a drink of water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the train left me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was left without anything, without-- even without documents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "All I have is-- is that birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, it's fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We need people in the coal mines here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll have you work in the coal mines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I figured now I am saved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am already-- finally I'll have a place where I can be legal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But before you do that, you have to go for a-- for a medical exam.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to a-- so he gave me the address where I go for medical exam.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I come to that place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a big sign with a big eagle with a swastika.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "NSDAP, which is Nazi party-- Nationalsozialistische Deutsche Arbeiterpartei-- was the acronym.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was already a-- a translator.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was-- he always had a translator for these foreign workers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he examined me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had to strip naked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He noticed I'm circumcised.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He noticed that something is-- but he asked the translator he should ask me whether I had some operation when I was a kid on my genitals.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- so I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As far as I remember, my mother told me-- she said I had some infection.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "No suspicion that I am a Jew at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "God was with me, apparently, [LAUGHS] watching over me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was-- I was allotted a place in the Gemeinschaftshaus on [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Scharnhorststrasse. ?] I remember either 13 or 19.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't remember the exact number there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were all foreign workers.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
